The '''tibanisphere''' was the layer of [[Tibanna/Legends|tibanna]] that existed on a [[Gas giant/Legends|gas giant]]. Due to its density, it settled to a specific layer in the [[Atmosphere/Legends|atmosphere]] where concentrations were greater.

